{"tid":295842,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人在曼谷唔知邊到，唔知點算","createTime":"2017-06-24T05:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T05:53:41.000Z","uid":13636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f4f8185b421d773a6db383318b75af18136bdfa2","tid":295842,"uid":13636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T05:37:44.000Z","msg":"我同我屋企人7個人去左曼谷旅行，我去緊個個火車市場個陣開始肚痛，應該因為前兩日我舅父佢地要食「地道」街邊泰國野食。<br />\n<br />\n我而加又暈又腳軟又發冷仲要好痛，但佢地要食海鮮仲想行埋個水上市場（勁遠市區），諗住叫我係車上面等佢地睇完，仲笑我邊到搵車俾我出返市區，問我係咪要包咖車自己出返去。佢地嫌我麻煩唔想為我一個影響佢地行程，我都能夠理解。但連我父母都話好貴由呢到出唔到去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我本身諗住可以uber出返去，點知呢到遠到無uber，仲要附近一咖的士都無。<br />\n<br />\n有無人可以俾啲建議我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45749feae156ffec06fbf335d8ff9b4a62d240d1","tid":295842,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T05:42:46.000Z","msg":"Mek Kong?"},{"pid":"17c4983b2bd80f173fcde4d4a7b5b08ae4710c85","tid":295842,"uid":13636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T05:47:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Mek Kong?</blockquote><br />\n唔係...係Damnoen saduak floating market附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f5f62b91cce177782d7736011e95a2a00a5920","tid":295842,"uid":82481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T05:51:24.000Z","msg":"down garb car apps,邊到都去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eace59acc61c4dc2903e8428bd852dfca45bcf8","tid":295842,"uid":13636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T05:53:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>down garb car apps,邊到都去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇睇先 唔該巴打"}]}